: 784.34px;"><img alt="" src="images/image29.png" style="width: 371.75px; height: 809.13px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: -24.79px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><h2 class="c13 c73" id="h.xa2nknw42nq5"><span class="c4 c2"></span></h2><h2 class="c41" id="h.45iuxyruxfw7"><span class="c4 c2">3.3 MODELAGEM ESTRUTURAL</span></h2><h3 class="c41" id="h.25nmwuf1lxm5"><span class="c7 c5 c2">3.3.1 Diagrama de Caso de Uso&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></h3><p class="c61 c56"><span class="c4 c2">Os diagramas de caso de uso mostram como atores internos e externos interagem com as capacidades do sistema. Incluem vis&atilde;o end-to-end e vis&otilde;es por dom&iacute;nio, alinhadas aos requisitos funcionais aprovados.</span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 20 - Diagrama de caso de uso do Dom&iacute;nio Dashboard e Reporting</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 297.69px; height: 253.47px;"><img alt="" src="images/image4.png" style="width: 297.69px; height: 253.47px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor</span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 21 -Diagrama de caso de uso do Dom&iacute;nio Fleet</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 288.11px; height: 307.65px;"><img alt="" src="images/image52.png" style="width: 288.11px; height: 307.65px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor</span></p><p class="c157 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c157 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c27 c157"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Figura 22 - Diagrama de caso de uso do Dom&iacute;nio HR</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 446.56px; height: 305.78px;"><img alt="" src="images/image31.png" style="width: 446.56px; height: 305.78px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor</span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 23 - &nbsp;Diagrama de caso de uso do Dom&iacute;nio HR</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 454.29px; height: 312.33px;"><img alt="" src="images/image31.png" style="width: 454.29px; height: 312.33px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor<br></span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><p class="c12 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 24 - Diagrama de caso de uso do Dom&iacute;nio Logistics</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 460.95px; height: 308.12px;"><img alt="" src="images/image62.png" style="width: 460.95px; height: 308.12px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor</span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 25 - Diagrama de Sequ&ecirc;ncia de Dom&iacute;nio Production</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 445.97px; height: 407.86px;"><img alt="" src="images/image36.png" style="width: 445.97px; height: 407.86px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor<br></span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 26 - Diagrama de Sequ&ecirc;ncia de Dom&iacute;nio Supply Chain</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 489.52px; height: 314.78px;"><img alt="" src="images/image39.png" style="width: 489.52px; height: 314.78px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor</span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><h3 class="c21 c73 c27" id="h.g9ph5c2nawcb"><span class="c7 c5 c2"></span></h3><h3 class="c41" id="h.jl7kkcthcqxl"><span class="c7 c5 c2">3.3.2 Diagrama de Componentes</span></h3><p class="c56 c61"><span class="c4 c2">O diagrama de componentes descreve a composi&ccedil;&atilde;o l&oacute;gica da solu&ccedil;&atilde;o com frontend, gateway, micro servi&ccedil;os de dom&iacute;nio, TenantResolver e infraestrutura compartilhada (RabbitMQ, Redis, Registry e bancos de tenant).</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c2">Figura 27 - Diagrama de Componentes</span></p><p class="c21"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 604.72px; height: 316.00px;"><img alt="" src="images/image41.png" style="width: 604.72px; height: 330.61px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: -14.61px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><h3 class="c47 c21 c16 c73 c27" id="h.4wtveqxrziob"><span class="c7 c5 c2"></span></h3><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><h3 class="c47 c21 c16 c73 c27" id="h.8xo57cglt829"><span class="c7 c5 c2"></span></h3><h3 class="c17 c16" id="h.sqglco2g0s8s"><span class="c7 c5 c2">3.3.3 Diagrama de Arquitetura&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></h3><p class="c65 c56"><span class="c4 c2">O diagrama de arquitetura consolida a vis&atilde;o de implanta&ccedil;&atilde;o e integra&ccedil;&atilde;o: AppHost, fronteira de acesso, servi&ccedil;os, Tenant Registry separado e bancos PostgreSQL isolados por tenant (inclusive em gestores/inst&acirc;ncias distintas).</span></p><p class="c48 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c2">Figura 28 - Panorama Geral do Diagrama de Arquitetura</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: -0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 583.11px; height: 162.89px;"><img alt="" src="images/image28.png" style="width: 583.11px; height: 162.89px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Figura 29 - Parte da Esquerda do Diagrama de Arquitetura</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 559.60px; height: 376.88px;"><img alt="" src="images/image28.png" style="width: 1350.92px; height: 376.88px; margin-left: -0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Figura 30 - Parte da Central do Diagrama de Arquitetura</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 460.78px; height: 460.78px;"><img alt="" src="images/image28.png" style="width: 1651.21px; height: 460.78px; margin-left: -679.11px; margin-top: -14.67px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><h2 class="c18 c73 c27" id="h.y9q13jry09ba"><span class="c4 c1"></span></h2><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 31 - Parte da Direita do Diagrama de Arquitetura</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 536.25px; height: 484.81px;"><img alt="" src="images/image28.png" style="width: 1735.88px; height: 484.81px; margin-left: -1199.62px; margin-top: -15.43px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><h2 class="c13 c73" id="h.cpwz3kxrnwqf"><span class="c4 c2"></span></h2><p class="c39 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><h2 class="c13 c73" id="h.f60r72p9ts8w"><span class="c2"><br></span><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"></h2><h2 class="c65 c73" id="h.loixnmt0hnd2"><span class="c4 c2">3.4 MAPEAMENTO OBJETO-RELACIONAL (ORM)</span></h2><p class="c56 c65"><span class="c4 c2">O mapeamento ORM documenta a correspond&ecirc;ncia entre entidades de dom&iacute;nio e tabelas, incluindo chaves, relacionamentos e observa&ccedil;&otilde;es de persist&ecirc;ncia para os contextos principais.</span></p><p class="c12 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 32 - Diagrama de Mapeamento de Objeto-relacional do IAM</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 569.99px; height: 342.79px;"><img alt="" src="images/image17.png" style="width: 569.99px; height: 368.83px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: -26.04px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 33 - Diagrama de Mapeamento de Objeto-relacional do Productions</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: -0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 604.72px; height: 189.33px;"><img alt="" src="images/image77.png" style="width: 604.72px; height: 201.12px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: -11.78px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><h2 class="c21 c73 c27" id="h.qqwn9t7kv73b"><span class="c4 c2"></span></h2><h2 class="c65 c73" id="h.ux4ssv9brloa"><span class="c4 c2">3.5 BPMN (BUSINESS PROCESS MODEL AND NOTATION)</span></h2><p class="c65 c56"><span class="c4 c2">Os diagramas BPMN descrevem o fluxo operacional de processos de neg&oacute;cio com foco em decis&otilde;es, exce&ccedil;&otilde;es e hand-offs entre &aacute;reas. Nesta vers&atilde;o, os processos priorizados s&atilde;o inbound e execu&ccedil;&atilde;o de OP.</span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c2"><br></span><span class="c4 c1">Figura 34 - Diagrama de business process model and notation</span></p><p class="c21"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 604.72px; height: 429.33px;"><img alt="" src="images/image5.png" style="width: 604.72px; height: 450.96px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: -21.63px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c13"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><p class="c12 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Figura 35 - Diagrama de business process model and notation</span></p><p class="c18"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 604.72px; height: 382.67px;"><img alt="" src="images/image46.png" style="width: 604.72px; height: 401.30px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: -18.63px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><p class="c39 c27"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><h1 class="c47 c16 c73 c118" id="h.webjqe2q78vu"><span>4. </span><span class="c7 c5 c2">DOCUMENTO DE ESPECIFICA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DE INTERFACES (DEI)</span></h1><p class="c13"><span class="c4 c2"></span></p><h2 class="c65 c73" id="h.55mpacl3le2m"><span class="c4 c2">4. 1. WIREFRAMES</span></h2><p class="c65 c56"><span class="c4 c2">Wireframe &eacute; uma representa&ccedil;&atilde;o visual simplificada de uma interface digital, utilizada para planejar a estrutura, a disposi&ccedil;&atilde;o dos elementos e a navega&ccedil;&atilde;o de um sistema antes do desenvolvimento. Seu objetivo &eacute; definir a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es e a experi&ecirc;ncia do usu&aacute;rio, sem focar em detalhes visuais como cores, imagens ou estilos gr&aacute;ficos.</span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 36 - Wireframe da Tela de Dashboard Operacional (In&iacute;cio)</span></p><p class="c21"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 604.72px; height: 296.00px;"><img alt="Figura 35" src="images/image72.png" style="width: 604.72px; height: 296.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c49 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c1">Figura 37 - Wireframe da Tela de Recebimento de Cargas / NF-e</span><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 582.11px; height: 284.80px;"><img alt="Figura 36" src="images/image42.png" style="width: 582.11px; height: 284.80px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c12"><span class="c4 c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c12 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Figura 38 - Wireframe da Tela de Workbench de Associa&ccedil;&atilde;o de SKUs</span></p><p class="c21"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 604.72px; height: 296.00px;"><img alt="Figura 37" src="images/image20.png" style="width: 604.72px; height: 296.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c18 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><p class="c12 c27"><span class="c4 c1"></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Figura 39 - Wireframe da Tela de Saldos de Estoque / Lotes de Materiais</span></p><p class="c21"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 604.72px; height: 296.00px;"><img alt="Figura 38" src="images/image64.png" style="width: 604.72px; height: 296.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Fonte: Produzido pelo autor.</span></p><p class="c62"><span class="c4 c1">Figura 40 - Wireframe da Tela de Centros de Trabalho (Work Centers)</span></p><p class="c21"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px -0.00px; border: 1.33px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 604.72px; height: 296.00px;"><img alt="Figura 39" src="images/image25.png" style="width: 604.72px; height: 296.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p class="c18"><span class="c4 c1">Fon